data.title: Royal Jewels of the World Message Board: Princess Sarvath al
data.text:
--Previous Message--

: Thank you, Barbara D. She does look lovely.

:

:

:

My pleasure, Paisley and yes, HRH looks always very lovely - and she definitely has 'her' very unique style !

http://media.gettyimages.com/photos/princess-sarvath-of-jordan-attends-king-carl-gustaf-of-swedens-60th-picture-id158106747

Princess Sarvath Of Jordan Attends King Carl Gustaf Of Sweden'S 60Th Birthday Celebrations.Gala Dinner At The Royal Palace, Stockholm. (Photo by Mark Cuthbert/UK Press via Getty Images)

http://media.gettyimages.com/photos/prince-hassan-of-jordan-and-princess-sarvath-of-jordan-attend-the-picture-id154429792

LUXEMBOURG - OCTOBER 19: Prince Hassan of Jordan and Princess Sarvath of Jordan attend the Gala dinner for the wedding of Prince Guillaume Of Luxembourg and Stephanie de Lannoy at the Grand-ducal Palace on October 19, 2012 in Luxembourg, Luxembourg. The 30-year-old hereditary Grand Duke of Luxembourg is the last hereditary Prince in Europe to get married, marrying his 28-year old Belgian Countess bride in a lavish 2-day ceremony. (Photo by Andreas Rentz/Getty Images)

http://media.gettyimages.com/photos/prince-el-hassan-bin-talal-of-jordan-and-princess-sarvath-el-hassan-picture-id102371061

Prince El Hassan bin Talal of Jordan and Princess Sarvath El Hassan of Jordan attend the wedding of Crown Princess Victoria of Sweden and Daniel Westling on June 19, 2010 in Stockholm, Sweden.

Here you can see, how parts of the saree are used to cover the hair/head

http://media.gettyimages.com/photos/queen-noor-and-princess-sarvath-el-hassan-of-jordan-at-the-funeral-of-picture-id3159472

DELFT, NETHERLANDS - MARCH 30: Queen Noor (L) and Princess Sarvath el Hassan of Jordan at the funeral of the Queen Mother Princess Juliana at Nieuwe Kerk on March 30, 2004 in Delft, The Netherlands. Princess Juliana died at age 94 as a result of pneumonia on March 20th at her home in Soestdijk, Netherlands. (Photo by Michel Porro/Getty Images) Message Thread:
